{"tid":1269260,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[求分析] 發夢見到個小朋友俾人搜身","createTime":"2019-06-30T13:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T15:01:50.000Z","uid":165752,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a6f1ea3a24cee1ac84e35665c6809018dd53d07","tid":1269260,"uid":165752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:44:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的，啱啱發咗個惡夢<br />\n有個小朋友行行下街俾人搜身<br />\n全身俾人愛撫完之後<br />\n覺得赤赤痛要求驗傷<br />\n當然真係驗到有傷<br />\n大家都好清楚小朋友係俾人輕撫<br />\n但小朋友就記唔係點整親<br />\n含糊其辭咁話俾人摸完就見痛<br />\n而摸嗰個就好遺憾<br />\n要進入紀律聆訊/司法程序<br />\n呢個惡夢真係好恐怖呀<br />\n<br />\n請問呢個夢<br />\n喺現實生活可唔可能發生"},{"pid":"d33b94886949d73337f84a34168daa2a1e77a8b2","tid":1269260,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:51:12.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"2e6b777f96a3ca36295d85a6190b165a8e171ed8","tid":1269260,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a150c178c07a94e00424244b329e7e7e9199c0c9","tid":1269260,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:54:29.000Z","msg":"唉屌, 係咪又精神病人"},{"pid":"7d865fabe9d86226b39b2538db326b215102409c","tid":1269260,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"摸骨"}]}